MES : Manufacturing Execution System is a term used to describe systems that track and manage all aspects of a job in real time while it is in the execution phase 
or in process. It may include resource management, capacity scheduling, maintenance management, statistical quality control, laboratory information management, process
management, data collection, plant wide document management and process optimization.
制造执行系统（MES）是指在作业执行阶段或过程中实时跟踪和管理作业各个方面的系统。
它可能包括资源管理、产能调度、维护管理、统计质量控制、实验室信息管理、流程管理、数据收集、全厂文档管理和流程优化。
	1. Collect various data from factory - Status of material, product and equipments; 
	2. Provide real time and accurate information;
	3. Data consolidation and analysis;
	4. Assist manager making right decision;
I : Resource management include FOUP Mgt., Labor Mgt., WIP Tracking, EQP Mgt., Recipe Mgt., Reticle Mgt.;
II: Quality management include Q-Time, EQP contamination, OCAP, SPC, Engineering Data Collection, Spec Mgt.;

