AMHS: Automated Material Handling System
	I : Provide the safe store environment for wafers and reticles.
	II: Assist the wafers and reticles be delivered to the right place at right time automatically and speedily and safely.
	
(1) Stocker : is a safety temporary storage area, and close to bay, easy to carry out to process EQP. Wafer Stocker & Reticle Stocker ; General Stocker & Tower Stocker;
(2) OHS : Over Head Shuttle is a transport EQP that travels on the clean room ceiling with linear motors. It travels for interbay transportation cleans room or between multiple clean rooms
		  Achieves high handling volume and quick-turn around time from bay to bay.
(3) OHT : Over Head Transfer is a transport EQP that travels on the ceiling to transport directly between a stocker and production EQP with linear motors.	
		  Archeves high handling volume and quick-turn around time from tool to tool by direct transportation.
		  
RTD : Real Time Dispatcher decide which lot is the best for the EQP 
	  Based on 1.Lot Priority, 2.Stay Time, 3.Remain Q-Time, 4.Critical Ratio((CLIP-NOW)/Remain Layer), 5.APC, 6.EQP Season, 7.EQP Loading Balance, 
	  8.Process Setup Time, 9.Batch Loss, 10.Line Balance, 11.Same Recipe...

